\int_{\frac{-\pi}{2}}^{\frac{\pi}{2}}|\cos2x|d(\sin x)
\int_{\frac{-\pi}{2}}^{\frac{\pi}{2}}|\cos2x|d(\sin x) =\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}}|\cos2x|d(\sin x)+ \int_{\frac{\pi}{4}}^{\frac{-\pi}{2}}|\cos2x|d(\sin x)
+\int_{\frac{-\pi}{2}}^{\frac{-\pi}{4}}|\cos2x|d(\sin x)+\int_{\frac{-\pi}{4}}^{0}|\cos2x|d(\sin x)
